  "reference_number": "RUS2743",
  "remarks": "\nTHE MAIN DIRECTORATE OF DEEP-SEA RESEARCH OF THE MINISTRY OF DEFENCE OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION is an involved person under the Russia (EU Exit) (Sanctions) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: THE MAIN DIRECTORATE OF DEEP-SEA RESEARCH OF THE MINISTRY OF DEFENCE OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia through carrying on business as a Government of Russia-affiliated entity. \n",
